items.title: Awesome Zsh Plugins
items.content_text:
### Plugins / [superconsole](https://github.com/alexchmykhalo/superconsole) - Windows-only

*   [lsd (wintermi) (‚≠ê6)](https://github.com/wintermi/zsh-lsd) - Override `ls` and `tree` commands with [lsd (‚≠ê15k)](https://github.com/Peltoche/lsd).
*   [lsd (z-shell) (‚≠ê13)](https://github.com/z-shell/zsh-lsd) - Replaces `ls` with [lsd (‚≠ê15k)](https://github.com/Peltoche/lsd).
*   [penmux (‚≠ê2)](https://github.com/mfulz/zsh-penmux) - A session manager plugin meant to be used for penetration testing sessions and tracking the terminal sessions to be used in reports.

### Completions / [superconsole](https://github.com/alexchmykhalo/superconsole) - Windows-only

*   [kubectl (chrishrb) (‚≠ê4)](https://github.com/chrishrb/zsh-kubectl) - Automatically loads completions for [kubectl (‚≠ê3.1k)](https://github.com/kubernetes/kubectl).
